snippet.title: WandereGun (now DuelingGun) - beta testing
snippet.description:
WandererGun is a indiegame I'm working, the beta will be released this sunday for everyone to play and test in itch.io.

See you with updates soon.

For more info you can follow in:
Tumblr: https://gamedev-challenges.tumblr.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GamedevChallen1
